Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gihon1進入預定軌道位置
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由空間位相雷達對質量進行再測定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤差修正Plus0.03
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記錄更新
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.91,0:00:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務保持
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊隊的情況呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破第一宇宙速度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將到達攻擊點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 馬上就要開始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我怎麼破壞那塊膽石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:00:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隕石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隕石才對 遙姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可是任務的領隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請有點領隊的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.29,0:01:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人感觸很深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到各國協同合作 向同一個目標努力時的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是拜學園長提供了加爾德羅貝的技術所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.94,0:01:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說要感謝這座KARAGAU天文台在剛啟動之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.10,0:01:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然探知到了那顆隕石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果撞擊到地面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅是艾亞利茲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周邊6個國家都會全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吃糰子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.02,0:01:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是貢品 現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星滅者離射出點還有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.47,0:01:45.04,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80}{\pos(310,443)}Meteor Breaker
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Force Wing 拋離
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:01.74,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80}{\pos(431,440)}Meteo Breaker   Ignition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星滅者 點火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有碎石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.47,0:02:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 會被大氣層燒盡的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}7
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}6
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.36,0:02:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Gihon1上檢測出異常向量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏離軌道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星滅者進路修正
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來不及了 即將命中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未能直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殘留有大塊碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.56,0:03:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因爆炸隕石再次加速
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.81,0:03:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突入大氣層
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路線是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計落下點是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風花市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 遙姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面會有第二波攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癡情!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:15.47,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日語中「地面」和「癡情」同音)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是地面 小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去試試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白 認證拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼天!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.56,0:03:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激活Materialise Zwei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤隕石中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Materialise Zwei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister愛莉卡的固有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們也在調查中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先代蒼天的青玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡也能使用她母親的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:04:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到不如說那才是蒼天之青玉本來的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要保護好大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拂曉!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼天之青玉…與Gihon1 正面衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是 愛莉卡·夢宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是 愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隕石成功擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.55,0:05:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mission Complete
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保護好了喲 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:13.90,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}第一幕　夢的延續
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～哎～是夢!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底做了什麼夢讓你變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss瑪利亞 剛剛那是夢嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把隕石「彭」地一下……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是拯救這個星球的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}風花期報--小螞蟻、拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}先代蒼天之青玉「雷娜」的親生女兒 立下大功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了Meister但還不夠學分的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾還是我的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去繞王宮跑五十圈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後把《乙女心經》從第12章到15章抄寫一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～是～哎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 下一個議題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於下個月在阿爾泰領召開的SALT戰略乙HiME限制公約
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:45.66,Note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（SALT:戰略兵器限制交涉會談）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.69,0:07:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧 命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前略 尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給現在不知道在哪裡的尼娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是一如既往的在心中給你寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以來已經過了一年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市已經恢復平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.21,0:08:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家每天都精神十足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白最近非常的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.67,0:08:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得很有女王風範了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我現在基本上沒能夠幫上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在正為成為一名出色的乙HiME努力學習中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候尼娜有心情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請過來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.22,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家一定能成為一個大家都能夠笑容滿面 快樂生活的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快點解散! 解散!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在城門前抗議的行為是被禁止的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是在行使勞動者的權利而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們見女王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.52,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You的發明Now one push呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的發明又增加了一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授 有關這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片落下形成的這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:24.25,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為Unknown所以要Let's study OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不知道所以我們要來研究 OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《勞動者的最低酬勞取消法案》通過 是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風花市工會堅決進行罷工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.06,0:09:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王的施政前途多災多難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然好像遭到反對意見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但考慮下風花的現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是適當的作法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下個月還有乙HiME限制的交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是一樣頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長 樣本回收完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.15,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長 Return學園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長 回學園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究員騎在教授背上算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託加爾老師也注意一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主任 就此結束 沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 再去一個地方好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 那個先放著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是確認一下痕跡就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話我這就去看看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們保持對乙HiME戰鬥防禦的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後退至加爾德羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像普通那樣回去不就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說總是這樣 開會還真是累人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.81,0:11:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您做得很了不起 真白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宮門前靜坐的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家還不肯離去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 是這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能取消
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是必要的改革
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人說不定會降薪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 不會有那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我是為什麼整天參加這個會那個會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大家都在擔心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你難不成和那些抗議的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 談過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了「笨蛋」兩個字了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就不能聽聽他們的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能隨他們喜歡去做嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.63,0:11:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光靠憐憫是不能施政的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白最近變了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你太一成不變了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那邊比起來樣子完全不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬌嫣的紫水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.92,0:12:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 一個人裝大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶也說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.84,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個子長高不代表長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡感覺像是受冷落而感到寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 不夠坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:58.06,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh～This face very cute呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh～這張臉蛋很可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 今天也不知道一個人跑哪去了 真白她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:16.73,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\c&H711AD6&}（警告：請不要給貓神大人投食 Meister舞衣）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 貓神大人是美食家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是貓神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我合影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 貓神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.51,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80}{\fad(300,0)}黑之谷 改名為 國立公園 貓神山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:31.55,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天已被預定一小時）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.15,0:13:31.55,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs80}貓神拉麵本店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 愛莉卡那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我是下定了很大的決心才通過那個法案
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以吵架了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣 好想快點吃拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 用不著太鑽牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白已經足夠這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有鑽牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 女王大人 貓神拉麵一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓神大人的也很快就來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很燙 要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶～舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關奴獸宿主解除武裝的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝那邊也沒有空閒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要全員解除有點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼小的孩子也持有奴獸 總覺得太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵會泡漲喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.07,0:14:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.75,0:14:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是上次的隕石嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分析它的成分 調查它的組成
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有想知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.09,0:14:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是准將她們說過的神秘的軌道變更
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留她還沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有聯絡過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 GEM通信或重粒子通信都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:01.82,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在途中Get pretty girl了～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是在途中遇到美眉了～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.23,0:15:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就去聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 Meister維奧拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣 再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不是已經吃了很多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會吃不下晚飯的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飽了倒頭就睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.16,0:16:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.52,0:16:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留姐姐現在的位置是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有GEM的反應呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也Nothing呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 快到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次物質化反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強大 這決不是舞斗服或是奴獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey～大家Look
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:16:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 這不是貓神公園的居住區中央嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在加爾德羅貝的記錄上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是新型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通報風華宮 主任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡 我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫水 調動風花軍全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 向市民發出避難警報
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 愛莉卡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 快去找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒 命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了 幫我認證
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meister舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也用奴獸迎戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 戰鬥就交給乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把貓神大人帶回山上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 祝您好運!
