Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Meister舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悲劇的Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要被叫到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.49,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去幫助觀光客的避難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.64,0:18:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻貓怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑去哪裡玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白才是 一個人偷偷跑到這裡吃拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉唆 一開始還不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是吵架的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架以後再吵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放汝之力量 啟動蒼天之力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.78,Materialise,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\4c&H272FFE&}{\3c&HE58908&}Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:18:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 小螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼天!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 愛莉卡
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HiME的音樂啊！！！！愕天王見參!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦哦 學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然也請求加爾德羅貝支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 好吧 幫你一把
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HE58908&}Load Chrome Cartridge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.86,0:19:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡的蒼天之霹靂被破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的傢伙要怎麼辦好啊 主任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.53,0:20:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奴獸的話就該有奴獸宿主在才對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在乙HiME們的Grave Room裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者奪走了真白的金剛石 正往真祖之間前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.28,0:20:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也正趕往那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.64,0:20:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Materialise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…真祖大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這裡弄得一片狼籍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我現身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二三大人的反應正在加速下降
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼下去的話 學園長的認證會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動Emergency模式
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:21:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上把認證系統切換到那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那裡」是?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備用系統?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.03,0:22:04.46,Note4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surrogate System?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.80,0:22:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency模式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認證系統被切換到備用的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反省以前那種情況而製作的緊急備用系統
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主任 發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓地傳來了警報 真祖大人的反應消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追蹤的Miss瑪利亞也失去聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.59,0:22:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回來 學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖之棺有入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.49,0:22:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.29,0:22:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡沒能及時逃離的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.58,0:22:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請去救那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長 回加爾德羅貝去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 真白 比起那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:22:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME現在還是世界的中樞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:22:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再發生「那基」那件事就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.32,0:23:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.79,0:23:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是約好了要創造讓人們都能歡笑的國家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才在做身為王該做的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.55,0:23:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.38,0:23:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白的話就乖乖聽從我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.41,0:23:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把蒼天之力量還給吾之乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.49,0:23:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給她
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.47,0:23:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.07,0:23:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:23:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.17,0:24:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入侵者的位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.97,0:24:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 備用系統已經到極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.34,0:24:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 只有一次有效
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.39,0:24:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.08,0:24:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不向真白求助
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.31,0:24:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.31,0:24:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.40,0:25:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.50,0:25:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣 愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.91,0:25:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真祖大人被什麼人給破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.76,0:25:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.77,0:25:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙奪走了被封印的真白的金剛石
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.05,0:25:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.04,0:25:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.31,0:25:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.74,0:25:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.39,0:25:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.59,0:25:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.06,0:25:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.77,0:26:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.09,0:26:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白!
