Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.12,0:28:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於出OVA了呢 舞衣
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.96,0:28:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你究竟明白不明白什麼是OVA呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.95,0:28:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然知道
